---
const { email } = Astro.props;
---

<section id="contact" class="py-24 bg-black scroll-mt-24 w-screen left-1/2 right-1/2 -ml-[50vw] -mr-[50vw] relative">

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20">

    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-neutral text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium">
        Vamos conversar sobre como posso ajudar seu negócio com soluções em dados e Business Intelligence
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      
      <div class="text-left">
        <h2 class="text-white text-3xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight">
          Informações de Contato
        </h2>

        <p class="text-neutral mb-10 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Estou sempre aberta para discutir novos projetos, oportunidades criativas ou parcerias. Entre em contato comigo através de qualquer um dos canais abaixo.
        </p>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-12">

          <a href="https://wa.link/d2vdux" target="_blank" class="bg-slate-900/40 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all group">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-[#22c55e] text-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">📞</div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Telefone</p>
                <p class="text-[#22c55e] text-sm font-medium">(21) 99143-5429</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a href={`mailto:beloyasmin17@gmail.com`} class="bg-slate-900/40 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all group">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-primary text-xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 19.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07-1.916V6.75" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">E-mail</p>
                <p class="text-primary text-xs font-medium break-all">beloyasmin17@gmail.com</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/YasminBelo" target="_blank" class="bg-slate-900/40 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all group">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 font-bold group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">in</div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">LinkedIn</p>
                <p class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-medium">/YasminBelo</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>

          <div class="bg-slate-900/40 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-orange-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-[#f59e0b] text-xl">📍</div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Localização</p>
              <p class="text-neutral text-sm font-medium">Rio de Janeiro, RJ</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-4">Redes Sociais</h3>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <a href="https://wa.link/d2vdux" target="_blank" class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#22c55e] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:scale-110 transition-transform shadow-lg shadow-green-500/20">📞</a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/YasminBelo" target="_blank" class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:scale-110 transition-transform font-bold shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20 text-sm">in</a>
            <a href={`mailto:${email}`} class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:scale-110 transition-transform shadow-lg shadow-primary/20">✉️</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-900/60 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 text-left shadow-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-8 tracking-tight">Envie uma Mensagem</h2>

        <form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" class="space-y-5">
          
          <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="d5898606-899e-40f2-8296-717108d58173">
          <input type="hidden" name="from_name" value="Yasmin Belo Portfólio">

          <div>
            <label class="block text-white text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Nome Completo</label>
            <input type="text" name="name" required placeholder="Seu nome completo" class="w-full px-4 py-3.5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50 text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary transition-all placeholder:text-slate-600" />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label class="block text-white text-sm font-semibold mb-2">E-mail</label>
            <input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="seu@email.com" class="w-full px-4 py-3.5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50 text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary transition-all placeholder:text-slate-600" />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label class="block text-white text-sm font-semibold mb-2">Mensagem</label>
            <textarea name="message" required rows="4" placeholder="Descreva seu projeto ou como posso ajudá-lo..." class="w-full px-4 py-3.5 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50 text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-primary focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary transition-all placeholder:text-slate-600 resize-none"></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="w-full py-4 bg-primary text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:brightness-110 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-primary/25 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 group">
            <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">Enviar Mensagem</span>
            
          </button>

        </form>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>
